                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18180909-159-off867 t18180909-159-cd868"></join>, four curtains, value 20s., and two sheets, value 10s., the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18180909-159-victim1258" type="victimName">
                           Mary 
                           Williams
                        <interp inst="t18180909-159-victim1258" type="surname" value="Williams"></interp>
